    <stitle>NEWAY AD-123/246 DRIVE AXLE AIR SUSPENSIONS - MAINTENANCE - 50,000 MILES OR 1 YEAR MINIMUM</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>50,000 MILES OR 1 YEAR MINIMUM</title>
        <para>At 50,000 miles or 1 year, or when servicing vehicle brake system, inspect suspension components per 5,000
            mile inspection. Also check all other suspension components for any sign of damage, looseness, wear or
            cracks. Replace any damaged parts to prevent failure or equipment breakdown.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
